name: Osyotr - Steampunk
description:
This tune was complete in 2010. 
After that - I stopped making music for 12 years...
No matter what I did all this time - there was no success.
Now I know why.
And I'm here to continue. To keep doing what I'm in this world for.
And I will do it to the end.
This final project will pick up right where previous left off.
This release will mark the beginning of work on reminding the world what music is.
And how important it could be.
The wait won't be long, I`m here to stay.

Your Osyotr.
